@TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5112
@bearerToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ==================================================
### STATISTICS ENDPOINTS - Key Indicators and Reports
### ==================================================

### 1. Get Summary Report (Comprehensive dashboard)
# Returns all key indicators:
# - Statistics by country (providers and services per country)
# - Total providers and services
# - Total countries covered
# - Average hourly rate
# - Most expensive and cheapest services
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

###

### 2. Get Providers by Country
# Shows how many providers offer services in each country
# Returns:
# - List of countries with provider counts
# - Total providers
# - Total countries where services are offered
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/providers-by-country
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

###

### 3. Get Services by Country
# Shows how many services are available in each country
# Returns:
# - List of countries with service counts
# - Total services
# - Total countries
# - Average hourly rate across all services
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/services-by-country
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

###

### ==================================================
### EXAMPLE WITH AUTHENTICATION FLOW
### ==================================================

### Step 1: Login to get token
# @name login
POST {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Step 2: Use the token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### Get Summary Report with auto-extracted token
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Providers by Country with auto-extracted token
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/providers-by-country
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Services by Country with auto-extracted token
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/services-by-country
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

